FBIS4-59090 "drnes091_j_94041" FBIS-NES-94-091 Daily Report 10 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Russian Foreign Ministry Calls For Cease-Fire Russian Foreign Ministry Calls For Cease-Fire EA1005190694 Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 1500 GMT 10 May 94 EA1005190694 Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network Arabic BFN [Text] The leadership of federal Russia has called on the two sides fighting in Yemen to immediately halt all military operations. It said in a statement issued by the Foreign Ministry that whatever the differences between the disputing parties and whatever ends they had in mind could not constitute a justification for bloodshed and fratricidal strife or the suffering of the Yemeni people, nor justify the destruction of what is new.
